HEADWORD: Cucurbitaceous
<hw>Cu*cur`bi*ta"ceous</hw> <pr>(-b⟦icr⟧*t⟦amac⟧"sh⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F. <ets>cucurbitac⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to, or resembling, a family of
